      "content": "i feel like everyone just tells me \"don't do it\" without actually explaining why. if the garlic is naturally thinng the blood and the kale is doing the same thing, won't that just create a steady state? if i slowly taper off the warfarin while ramping up the garlic and the green juices, wouldnt that be a much safer way to transition to a natural lifestyle? it seems like it would be more controlled than just quitting cold turkey.",
